  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FEVisitor
    Visitor interface for FENode nodes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Annotation
    Customizable annotation attached to a TypeStruct or Function node.
    DummyFENode
    Unsupported AST node.
    FEContext
    A FEContext provides source locations and other context for a front-end node.
    FENode
    Any node in the AST, usually created by the front-end's parser.
    FENullVisitor
    Implementation of FEVisitor that always returns null.
    FEReplacer
    Replaces nodes in a front-end tree.
    FETypedVisitor<T>
    typed version of FENullVisitor
    FieldDecl
    Defines a list of fields within a package; it's like a global variable, but it is private to the package.
    Function
    A function definition.
    Function.FcnInfo  
    Function.FunctionCreator
    Factory class to generate new Function nodes.
    NameResolver
    NameResolver helps translate the name of a struct, function, or variable from the simple name (without package name) to the full name (with package name).
    Package
    Similar to a namespace in C++, contains private fields (global variables local to the package), structures and functions.
    Parameter
    A formal parameter to a function.
    Program
    An entire Sketch program.

    SymbolTable
